title: How To Stop Living In Fear With Bart Pietrzak
itunes:title: How To Stop Living In Fear With Bart Pietrzak
description: Bart Pietrzak joins the Underdog Empowerment podcast as the first guest on the show to discuss how to overcome fear completely so that you can feel good just being you. Bart combines mental toughness with self-actualization.
content:encoded: Bart Pietrzak joins the Underdog Empowerment podcast as the first guest on the show to discuss how to overcome fear completely so that you can feel good just being you. Bart combines mental toughness with self-actualization.
itunes:subtitle: Eliminate fear and step into your real self.
itunes:author: Zachary Babcock
